title: JPL, NASA, Japan Quake Displacement, Japan, March 14, 2011
name: JPL, NASA, Japan Quake Displacement, Japan, March 14, 2011
description: The point shapefile shows preliminary results of land displacement for different parts of Japan due to the massive quake. The displacement is both horizontal and vertical. The displacement in space ranges from just a fraction of a meter to more than 4 meters (24 ft).
